    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained. The exterior paint retains a strong shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small, visible scratch on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is clean and well-preserved, showing only light wear on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, the car is solid; it has been serviced regularly, the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as expected. All electronics and climate control systems are fully functional. It is a reliable, honest car that reflects its history of careful ownership despite a few cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 34000.0,
